ks.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/5K2BDNyYqgfzzsDm8eja5XPA_ZhFW5ILX-vx8T-htcoqDSOo4YoDGlDQR3DzArxyqimCnjRAqmzyjrTuZhqtcYw1rSQtDFzk2kle9Nj1fWAAaOW9HXgt8bUXDq-HlcX5DkuJiL5KDeEH8v3B-O8DJuJKZY1Lo0L3CN3nTBWp2d7yQu0J7HZifgg2jpBSag0H7n8585GbySSeapQQL0vmHo_f99d2eGNpqbNMBIUZbNqWQPNlmvNGrO2JnXpD5A2wFhMy1SkPbahAmpaDkofMAj0YyA3DeOyZt93Dl9IRAkD0P0gCrjExyi8qWgXRChATb4iM0OwAbatN8fKcEsRyQ5tptQB70tMK4tzGVBPNlo0j4xuiC0fcP2eUfzHgK6UwSYVrp32BmLTmg14MrLUhCLY-deIdvPF2MObFzqEPl_Qq7kkrCFkd6M5d2FZniKyz9VgO8RptijjUsdiK_Vg1lU4iI4oY_VZe0tMRXDutxH2S5W_uirpdOmwghFXrXTxoGXixbfhFXWachAs9lBdmrwqj1VYX99wIPZiGNlHgRzHQ_hIMRNWMxmPTQnkENxutM3DgyLtTOT-cATyo7C6W17N9jw0bdysl-jtbb2VdK4RwnGNe_thuQ9Y_8q-j2G_XO0z_Kr0z6xMDcOjP1aiqmZquC9sVY9BdcydOyD0c4HJkzLfW9ZA1OZnveUG4dQssyGBDhyozneZytGwA488-AgHDHCezIxt4tyNrqSfZ-PSjFH4b1pa9ttNCYHOoRIHQH32wp_N5LDvrDZEdN2f8BSrhqwuVvtZPbYI0a68pNI2pgeIIYLrzNdTdia9flU3QeNy-y2symqL3mb0OYazNHHep_ln4v34v6elepw_hdtJatbi901xHbn5SRp-pkJarFw4ZEZwZ94WEACNlTJW8ujfDlTb5dc_jBUuNMQ9ZO3lUL0TNvoisniQ/pcaz3HMQmiKjtxcchpli_7_q-zO08ghJ/7" target="_blank"&gt;批准率下降到43％&lt;/a&gt; 。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/WXPlHXHA4ebULy8W8fybhOkQ9Q0MGKG1FN1uXtC8YIdjmU4Vd99Dou26fToz6ipGjVtZlkhMAkxpr5ipCmTrlljZhgMWz95jjzW6dt-ehSNaJ4h_UFgyOMmaM5gwgyp2WSC85Xnow9-fN23fbdBZK_F-5n-20x_zWu9VHHgVQ0MTXnMrMiORd6s2D14pNGulH7eHza3qK2dduyo4l5ejYaowi160791YhEVKLNFzZjzrOrGelZJ267ogTSUSEVDn_kp3F14r1uqdjoi9eSSPZ1FTQbDTgdQcP9SMWnArn5Pu9rJAmkrB8i1c4xY9P8oiPYllmm9Nws_KfEleGH4hmK_0HGGguy6cv8u5LARmcMEcVdL4L1NRYt0Eng/GT2uT5P8wWpFrgJZom4iZmtf0ASbSizS/7" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iyPBUqor7psU/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iyPBUqor7psU