攻击的增加，投资策略将同样快速地创新。加入高管，例如Uber的Dara Khosrowshahi，包括Jeffrey Katzenberg和诺贝尔奖获得者Jennifer Doudna（由彭博社的Emily Chang和Tom Giles领导）的投资者，讨论如何导航危害并通过技术的快速变化造成的机会。 6月4日至5日在旧金山&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/kKXWe9T6UZW9cIrWqIp6VyQb7lasRJi2v7jf-gIpEzqmiqq9WmWotGf6Hnrc7cjkeuA4OtjvXsvG9EVmtKVuJntDUgk5B-mtHEKvKYg-ESTvy0cQsIbfe1u-o9LJT9or4fttxPCWgfn9Jceko9pyaW2NDsRoI8VWLyE5gxsNMYsmkf0C-2IBas3QQY6yZpploLdiNxwwfPh03RqwCt_o-eY07Y6vbDJHvMUqRjZn342DEyoAStwSRWH4WFepr82eZOUABkgv-2GO29JAeLoFEXG7eOEO60bvo9KI_0CYgAPFCbyYh1Z1PqRGHqr-Zl0EWiojiONlJ1ODj1-iRBIEL2if7GkE56tZGQFQZbRZ0lXNmK8ApmoJwVKs9DSi4ePk2_RKRfBHn6uflzq2vlrry9V0dMIpUQLKVN-nX4PnBPxY7zmZ9JmZWNBa9l-iHqZHglpbSxeDSkozUhp5weweT5xrOm7Frf2Di15yZ9dxW3MARzYEhHfnucyTOgMeEbxZWs3x5ACNVy1FXu-MGwf8XshKCdvD9LtlN783RN19jsiqZM9w5Fj2_V_N0_ryXlhgxNOss0YwIm87JJnQMgAp4ZaGGfn2hTxzAiAMC1e6LCFScJLvy1yRI8T400wk5vMl0srn1Ze5kMZV0XrTSJ1rFs3J1kkRrguUfg_UT8fCF8RkgQqtavfdRcuKlRUOkU3sKCz5owtLQS3tolA19Qs2cjIxMExFWJd29zTxfefHrKcTwKpQ3Ceutvf8VZmFkB_AmVcUN4IAN_E/LF4_eL5soDQCp9tXESuQdMzpb1zfGxj5/7" target="_blank" title="链接到网站"&gt;注册&lt;/a&gt;活动。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;来自彭博社的更多信息&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;在您的收件箱中&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/9Q8potjN5JdR1a_jUTpC2vjdZoCymiM6-OJHdjr-CE-8u2gsOcMjP5D3wF9blvUU02RvBJ7AR63YMMv0WBp0ybM7oJKhQ_OVxPwd5Y5w-RBBzdq39gj-6dHUJMHF0c5hSCfel9lM3LKoHEUwQ2qjzKuYJTxbvmmjr3fkJPEDx4JSJJhzkYTV0ffGLDj5DGMdaQdVRJKoeLn098UEmAh8ZtypbNvJpIuhKmi9M94hN23pTgUULDkUV54JRsVjmPmGh9juGvnJvlM0GpIuezcmtaof0gurcDX6Elu6TK8Jeg