aNoltVFxAr539YUuvBUuXS-3-6AJtvXc/fecVNsIJAdbg1OvILD35l-TtyW-zh-Fl/7" target="_blank"&gt;构成了义务&lt;/a&gt;。至于财政部长斯科特·贝斯特（Scott Bessent），他向美国的贸易伙伴&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/r7cGYwNhnxeD_bfR4gSpB_lSR1S-io_NhRJl4OtaCJOpCfAofXn2CdLzdunJwyVSYrpybxVYTpLBFTjy9dXVaJmxhvS7dfH2AONNQYlkFe_eE26aJNdCbDRgxs_UtJ73lLl2btAQC0QJ5oED-cM1orgG_s8s5Tt2tz4ytdUCS7Icef0jOmeSVUjK40MxIju-TWT61H8sdZRQ68ugzLA9rDUEbBNr9tpzyQaiuibzsh5PzQS2wcMD-TEvr5CR4CiGVTqgdEaTI99sSgPk6wLiJNsaFvF2N1BEdfWeczTUrip2maN5yOpGON1t0U8NC9aFNHaZ-XJ8a_6uw-IFe5wmNq99FDZJAGCbPfx3kRaloUM_7KrsHYnmL6orqCU/3lyG3fKxgBdjWpw6yqGsQZFx6qQg9TRA/7" target="_blank"&gt;提供了这一建议&lt;/a&gt;：“只要您不进行报复，这就是这个数字的高端。”同时，一系列关税使&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/dkhLg2vVa3PUO_Wek1cV_-o5RAel2A4QuqQIDR1cIG9UUVV_PKYXen_6oXr1suxV7Lc1f4OENSIH9iFU0bCogs3hKwFESBqGJnHiQqOMGjRLGjCTla_On7OZX5jy7zpDQXyRXefvpiP4Q7_Zl1z3HZ9DmleISuOSxpLDgr-HcqqDCoXGFuSfncr4H2niVVvTpBBYEIP83Ys25VtOOYjP9Djpg0wBwO2SHmD_IfGCavndL2o3MqEIP7hGzFnXpHC6am-X1BdOfFmHhLFrNctUgbwlfpdbfgBZmUq8NCKFtjYA1vPt7s10UvqudPzk9NPhGCK3OR-n2rhec8vT179PCfkD3A0wYwPBbJYcjgrIyXHT6Sb3gDot9hhiQVs/0OwYV6AnkCu4x3ZvZLbD4wwCor-2k1oQ/7" target="_blank"&gt;美联储陷入了艰难的位置，&lt;/a&gt;因为它与增长和通货膨胀有关。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;全球金融市场&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/DU9czY3Q8WIxH5STgE8oAK9TDbfFnbATMGTQbMb9rkakk5DHG7U5dfPUiT3xzDTVwcsxtmllRURKBxyplivU_ub-zBjazEYFSj5FmowcMR_sQo52m4Jcp6jusTtdhuGFt2HdVeFpGJaOwb8HkXXyDwAtXfTD04WH28SDqaQ-ywBYwmk6Ekux70_cPKL0l_B0TzzTdQ3S2hQKJxd_N3PM5ax6WpX0TdsWDeQbZAWzRKviuYI-cqZSjsQspgIlpejF7cP0DhiVw6X3NK59BKGhQgAFUZUjhSfoV5-uaHuffw3GjlH4qMTzpmO8pmvhhetxA5z7EtxH8eV_vrb3u7kBaHFPCBsz4cYRQAe4xOSqYBFNKLPV490C-pd8VUk/sI98iBdsUSmOD3Z_1XS5922O0VxB_-c1/7" target="_blank"&gt;也做出了巨大的反应&lt;/a&gt;，而美国的期货却陷入了&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/yzg06M9vXA-loQBgS87FUXHVEjrydUdT7CZC1qATbn1wilpDXnoHVRglR6SjCABiJAU4KvtzkrFKgAhUxMdM3Stbs381snnHeYatdccadnYGyhwBgxEfkSUZuBNvdsUBaVjce4TJHsjrV7L94IjZRXd7E_wKLwVFr_4U4LSedsMG95PqOaK9_Y-QiG0-2yPsWASeqI3i7_n4N_vqRJMHle782yDGc3U82t5moCFVIBNb6H5TPz8rzpbq61qblWaLkMFEEbP1sNJfI3eRJALpvmXrLW7LSc_mN2OTYNz8iYIbdgiTrJVQc24T8OW_68oxVZ_dMJ1ifKZwGq58o-h2QICX9e1fab7KHrBJtlFFEH3KT6DMRTedHmifZ4M/14YfjbUk99HCqzqUMR4c7W5sYlM6JksA/7" target="_blank"&gt;全面的贸易战&lt;/a&gt;可能使美国经济陷入经济衰退的担忧。避风港的资产再次以黄金跳来跳去，取得了纪录。由于这一切都可以，这是&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/2aQbU6gv7qygks8iHMjGj_sJAr1ZiViEQvIyk5LNfJ-8LgaKlhrVlTTwOVxRYDXeR2sOUmRM-X9BA1w5XVwlS7hpk9k-_j3R1oM0MKu6k3kFcF4pkzK7P1GWNB4wvvZATXPFjMV5sAnBSQqHMDcE7TcZet8vYarIsaMv2bcnjK1mWp7gCVU-GzGh4B7hvhtpNvBc_JtWjcMgE5sZkOffEQbj23hrvS8y5SZPJYl9dEfFzdYrErybyh53pV4o_YzblNiRLFNH4dBo1DWFW_36cnudEVTXHTdr-WhrevYvuAiIoqUMxOoXh3qX_eyiKjkVFEYxL7nsXGPdhFpczfXq7f_b92au3z3bh_Pzri6mKiHh4G7sqNvic6jo_wA/xuEa3tAHb9UrHUIvaF9x8YpGVsh5R_Z_/7" target="_blank"&gt;战略家和投资者对贸易措施的看法&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;贸易战争&lt;/strong&gt;，关税威胁和物流冲击正在振奋企业并传播波动。通过&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/WiuPafAwyvDPns4Vq1LLnXb8MTlPcONGlKAZnftnycv5uf7zt93Ye6Ti8XM2FsTWyfaGMZ_eaXxYvbgWDI7dWFg62bZ4QI8Ye4y5Y4LLOeSX5DDgFfqGWGuwBdHVCE7Z5DzfZBlyaG1qbV61QKsS9j-8WTpC5YbsU0Wct6uZEm1HPs8gohkmL29u91fVW2FcxpFHaoRP8R-Ujn208sZnSfhEpcvxuD0Y8lxcvk-nGxPWUSrhbtjGxGUU5pHTEHWQbOYpGfV4Gg2Ft9HajgbO0TRPZgQbk3RrZmPYrajeUxIb_UZfTRVVIhOA85-0QinNCJ2kqhTTuWoHEeeVVQ9QRKoXSaJftDFZatpI5w2aq7ohiLE_Vdr8KVnRs0c/myHhkbOeYSoUG56bsvwhCAWh_fifv99D/7"&gt;新闻通讯&lt;/a&gt;了解全球商务的新秩序。&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;参议院共和党人&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;也从DC发出消息&lt;/strong&gt;，推出了预算蓝图，旨在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/klVUVkMpeULUoxNsEKNfY2IUT9RNcq_DewTawWwa91sf7A8MefL8AbTcPA8bFmslURXvSKA95qZwf7SRcTqIDUeby31Tw3AelSlBTCZJsccDEvIHt3qS_TIrvO6A_yT2JDO