ymLtDLvKwX8PEDP_dVTfW0o3qK_R2D_2TABOrIrK99qH8aVPTgiCAysmEswPoo8uSY_LCCaPNwBhDk1b59rjLixElSGDoVOnnxuuED7sEQgKuAG8lOqbpxUuigpDLuEgUfp6sLZUuVzIT-gBRf3-lObG4HFPtQCyut64ZEKfuiKRejAn4ZVt4oXVrnQBR48s5pUCOVJ-fePd0U7igONBmj2i4CLWgjp3KfFREc9QOrLLIhDUT4GQjMe7ho/PrxVnoqfyQ2N2wuDCmBw_qyY0o_9cit5/7" target="_blank"&gt;关税配方&lt;/a&gt;全部与贸易赤字有关。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;美国最新的关税越来越有可能对中国的经济造成的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/kWfa5IpFTE3IbHpO2JI8l5mUovsuhQjpjqG5KdzImZyDEcY_P_KTm5txDfxzy_d3nZ18ql1ca2CLSBsP0x3t3mJtf1pmz18zMSsWY0JygvgHu_cqQi7KgHgDJfP6WduPNPN_LmikQA8rpPKJHX1quLsUPYV1RyRo4zuFMjsnv4i6u9NGrs5HcuiKrw9VE8uU0Zs1hW55cea_-e1OaaAuewE05eIEXZSQelmVn32WAAxDQLwxoUwU4TWXjkIQEmH-aolryvcVyqjRa68_o0BN6ZOpkNWzltv_aeTg97MJnx35AtnwSlCp6kTlBaictFolZW7maJVFSCwvrjmw7tEM8VvkJVEzXuU5jg0nkei4REVVEiIIBRR3SCaDtE8/_rfL78nvA2ic9HBBFBn3Z7M_n62oY3HP/7" target="_blank"&gt;打击比他在他的第一次贸易战争中遭受的更大&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;特朗普全新的关税&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/rd2nTGytEtP03Kqwee42MCcOpGa--TsQ9DsBgAJ7Q7SPJCyMy39TLhi0qR63vNBxXRxCab6tvrSiuVmNp8LM5EH_MsO3wSrnLgPjhNBOPr5tNVPuNcrq2mpyOAGOjOUDVuihkFdI1ZhRX9JUc48NqmbBnC_i9vPVEJpp_yi-tP5U4Jht8qFMBSYyIrakIGnKUIfW-zyYcbeLDYTTQKruzL3rstx0urEvbNWWaXy5vN1-y434UyW9yGc2KFLHJiZekeoVBkBBrCEfiDo2-Y0ZS2q1-YxPYRzj-ArKjk0No8v7JdH2k4Hxe7NE5BihVvsYtTPYYGUZfM0pmLf0mnVJRUz9c4gPvrBbw-qvPZJxhdPp85y61Ba15hNHBhI/b9XqJa5dgaOg1er6Cytw4qOeyexMSSI9/7" target="_blank"&gt;毫不费力&lt;/a&gt;，从&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/MRLtZ3haJ8PxE6WOp203sb4kWXkyBOYMoXVZGaTwXN9Yj8ISXt4NQ2y-QFuyVjkcllg5d2dj2OJEIgHup6UEOGWQIUIEMdeaqIF9YBndxm81Exy4f40QP67um5KxvlxsETyfPtStPj9xyWd4w8LGi5k0jzx2KYPE8CfL4o3AqSNl0aVbF5ApnOpPnjLzNTx3PyB0j4V2vvVnYtwVBqJr_N9x3a3sAqCMc0YAZA7oB3GcGeB5wHKHUDsqFGNaMOqPxAxEQlefECWuiDb0mLZkdGnzGJc8tRfQv9T09-n-Ccol8m3F8t4akpsdL-hqSQveMyR44jh--fQDbW15F7VT5CWTdVSk1QvSV9gFS-9lMHB_IIXeafWF7zbdB44/jYKMRKU_9TpIH3MwqbG8njM08Mnynv7L/7" target="_blank"&gt;朋友&lt;/a&gt;到&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/kCg57_uM-YRIaS2b-3vFrT08YRVJ0cvutrYAxxWSZ6lY1I7mjb4FRabnsfk-EmNv0Zr0pQb6bNzwRv1bxyaVQ0dNE2Xwux45oDOW0DUSuKEiwE-vmZvNtomCBIiAl-D_zvzpyLFgyET7fjLQ89e9Xz_HFMblY-UM_ryf7AgEwEct41GT2sVOBGgmobVwotsSPt_G3rdyl412pd4RnCEVt566UqLzmJnKtzH6e3d1TD4byE6IVEynByOpy8pdo4LS7O4hngQ2KOuEb0-jRNHK32FfKm-zJkpXs-VP19QmTqat_diWE6oIlNvSYT2C9dPeT8kic6EZfZ1xTF5zrtnc4k_Z9D5-BthNFsASwYIxNOcQ82-8lZByCnX4jng/JchIGwWGliFgKUMHKv6aSEBRLGT3z545/7" target="_blank"&gt;敌人&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;关税支持的国家&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;特朗普试图在周三将美国的经济时钟倒退到一个“关税支持的国家”，能够放​​弃所得税并充满财富。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;特朗普说，这不是分享1930年《 1930年平滑 - 霍利关税》的正统解释，这是大萧条的经济痛苦的主要因素，而是努力“ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/6yUV06bJ9ldtBQL6lHB-qjUIAwWS6KNKpgNLkv5Q67wrsGTwm-EbMaqiNpRg_L6RAhDJuDqhxUi4b6ZtQQZl7HMbqwMvxmWgB76__LJ_EE5WHiFAWAQ1d51sCEM8XUGbWgyRGzlF7P7Jh47a5bOVJd49gSoeXF6DrlVYn8oJgiG9KDitpYUy0-B4yS4SNwQuEVm9TVTnm2P-Uu_FFTN4vQqyXpHq74_S0jZUrIGX7FZtv12HvLhx1QJpuTknaplZ0mYdTS70UYBRejjyRGDk28qsZSfpBSWUxgFvrKGlcPLGz-iwgI6uMz8OPOwz9QTeuhQdRDSFOB-VViIdwxBf3GtlOL4vui3EAn-jihJ2O6veqeFjBMKarPejgYA/OVC5zYBvWKk440TW5fg9CrVRgZdoj037/7" target="_blank"&gt;拯救我们的国家&lt;/a&gt;”。他说，实际上，大萧条“如果遵守关税政策，他们将永远不会发生。”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;有了这一定罪，特朗普在白宫玫瑰花园仪式上揭幕了一揽子&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/0tjLHJeQj3DfHiIOlJIR-8k_oblbvFJXVLYo8WtNYUYwSwihWIolneid8oNjo8X_SoPsCiVxxbdQtSJdaDYUXuaofdCXOFUhAr5omPGNX8EhtrUozplXin4sVgxCGK-pDXSqmiKfZlkztiF_9ccn_Xeg_DAWzOvWcqIfrAoV2DH_g0unRGrSmZDoA5t0F3xta1OFXPGwqT5bs2pNp40psjvGONG1caYjNgiKYiViiDJSHkmjjcCgSnVG0Q5oXHv32AnD1oZlWm6JGrAnoox-3yC85HA63Vfd2zmoH1s2-z1EWTOBxP8SMuWU0NTFs8675gKF7EFsD5FV0xLCgltQccreLXfJaRWF6U5sMsfoCmG5_81bDIbQe6XsDgo/0oDrayb8bLUABVVKGfxSf-P9_7sGnzfw/7" target="_blank"&gt;关税&lt;/a&gt;远足甚至使&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/3VmhdO95negussRDEp0_Tm2FesnKadMIFyaMbypHo0_ugXDr66af033Y1vSZMfJ6tMZmJa-wemcJCBn6qknkKc2Fz1VrPiMawBs6POGR2MQne0OA1anSC31UH1nEeqfbCg-Df5HO_BUXyFupo2QedejRfmtdteW1ZrfjRIjnnNamCEOvOR9qtUO9RacCa--UrJxT-s8z-Klu8xjtlCqe7fukrxy0ZOAERpWA1CEiOHdAmuf4UHkrvEpKNykeGRM_AWTfWtr74Fb8-lGWK6H82ZioOMofZH34FEvgMKmsw-tReb5Hnu6i3oWSSwhAYIyLkfNAlzqyK98KKdphYYsJiB-pGD_hRm9lRkJgZr7dl9dKa8NpYmMVwwegEEk/EqN-Zw3IeudwkWTvwGiwrjZB2A0dwpaq/7" target="_blank"&gt;1930&lt;/a&gt;年的关税升起&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/nY05Yj9NREJZmi2zTZxNBWOASGdSKtgiT5-C1zc2cgkFdm1OJoO5TMT_zx-1CfJHJdlvzq7cOnvUSgK9fcoQTp12FxvE4ZHumZ4-yEkI7tYyGlhxOZx2ZXQQU2rw7QxvJVy-oUJhqNCRuj_c2-vibnrls0vC-jIWW8yL9J12pQAwRu1gP4Cdee7yBvjFpll6NF4X-BYK_8qBZPbkOzY1HDWe9ulANti9cIJqEp6Qt7401a1GvyxTitDU1J9uFlsoakMS1tfkmM4GTQ-K2K0sYGaWLuZ-ezfpTySRFM8oNHGc5UWA_JNRMlWvHm4VuluZH3vvyxmWH7Q2p-nHuCKPPGL5UXdpoZvU8gSd_3ScYNONfZOrZKTlci4wj0Q/Jg9D4Xq9cMzP_GoIo040rU53P7ovoUEg/7" target="_blank"&gt;。&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/aZxToB7VSc6BlS4Xl7Ik4HER2rxDoeyeOj6w2196mTwQMVgoQ3tPP7LmgxaSXJVCzFKeD3zCbeXYNnD952HuLit8sUdpXwXSADwI1bP3NzZKHViP6C5XFPklsLNJPrmwyquaIhQXRc6kWnzaxIpo5zvEI15p6CPnfeAQXLlQ9vIoss9Yht8z6Eb-Yo-B1n-eWuSBRckZl3JwES3EumlO1uY5PM16uGTSPrAjhdm-KiabGRhbDBpPGI29r0vjZa63nJrxtQXLCxCJyPAYxXDswYKyKxge7XdwjbZ3za-nHvaJ-ItFZx_D2qu3l6tGFQRx6xFTTaWtKHYR_shANW_dC5kkM02KYVx8DNymgYRO8fMXhXgo2EM3Bgi6wL4/iAUMuUxPDQxbhL66cPli9jdriur2m2AR/7" target="_blank"&gt;中国&lt;/a&gt;的34％互惠率将与前20％的Surtax结合使用，可赚取54％，而&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/qPDSBkfs-1ozFBOxmdGSYjfiECvg8m_dF5TYLW7lrsdOGfZqdPd3kBhI5uo6EoPgGyk3OzlOM33ehULeAbhywbWdinaGPB6pNbKN8kaMQhfZ8u7FS96-dmfkB5ynS6c-WiQSbsTfoQTKyJs0CN_lma7eMbitbzIWe79jIQ6qVd-UOYbAkCbA1xRA1Xv1bSemrrzEV1LoSwarow4bK-Y48F3bXvOZRij04JWei0okY5rKSg1D6SoTOLCMr6VcYL6LM4hBJWv7CBdplwPX0VaujyGxYmd4W4zIDBVXm1fdDygvbMuaAgvggpo37hM_93Xtidhgb3V8wXjTIMH4wYY23eaxX7hEYlqBavc1vGsuUzSsEeVOGngahTr88ic/t0Tf47Fo-_Tcm7tPl5nfT7OGcqJVX6oc/7" target="_blank"&gt;欧盟&lt;/a&gt;商品面临新的20％征税。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;这些数字是复杂的，在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/omxMSDc-AqB5v_dczEDdFSY_DHjl1mcgLiI2f4iXGvw9kgpfBnJeUnyVKWvnVDrJSEVAq4nmY1zsVyA-CJbSc6vEI4XD-lmbKUwUhXhAM9kVzDlfCVa_TDLlqu6lGsOviqNy0LD4Fg1MFb7JMStrvycTYoSJv8usosVGGDpu4zT-iWBR68_UT3fKkRAGCJ-NdXgqsYEDFtou8mC8riiFWfT8QLtR8Riz1kKt3sWop1I2ckwP2z2pD60TCjGoT5doH9-6vJrrePCAJQPBQQDKiPXFId6M0B8Udxs--5RYy4N2Qav1N5oFBq823GE8IEyNjvJ-JCdneu4pu_EVutHSeto6TyNvr8SjUvXkgFxY-x1KhUbhu79LrIs5zqI/fympsagpPGruLBXmP4Wxc8bZa0hMDIra/7" target="_blank"&gt;对汽车&lt;/a&gt;，铝制和钢等产品的部门关税的背景下，这些数字都在范围内或即将到来的产品。彭博经济学估计，随着先前的自动及时加息，这一宣布可以增加16个百分点，使美国的平均关税利率增加了约16个百分点。 Evercore ISI计算出的平均率达到29％，而平滑的Hawley水平为20％。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i95Eu58jQkgY/v0/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i95Eu58jQkgY/v0/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;无论最终统计，它都比大多数经济学家和投资者预期的要高得多。这是在股票的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/eU9ZsNomxXlfpA2iSWcdbRrC0_gZOOF94SLXryVPpHIYXNjxIQVmvlqFGS1MBlczyBIZxAQsL2n0ZWdoQDVY5SXGpBbknWFKf7u2w6MjUt_mR63VvKoOPFUcVNAhCJWibdOzaTovwLCM3N9IO4SmjsM8yUd2fePTX2FPXl50WspYwhuTV3aFmXV9CI_-DQYocjeJ57khLeUDt1byb2kRHCAXM2-gAX-Xopy4HYYH1wLIqWyXnc4fASLKNVVCxaR5XyLavjiNdZewZDgL_eSKCywwyQw6eWJZ8RH8Uw7MAQCtxOU3cx3Rx72Z7UwZAc3BUwCj_qOrcAauVS_KgfctY_pdS9pWJYKyYLvaVonSVj8yrbZBFSmo49PHTrk/dmeKf1TMX6hTAW9DJILeLUuk8cJZcyJb/7" target="_blank"&gt;直接鼻子&lt;/a&gt;中看到的。债券市场今年开始为四个美联储&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/ksx2GJ2-ZTBxrfUWjsIylw-AB50QRNEQiHeJMdZpX2J-Ed39i9omwx43pnQX6E9UHaYo-joqY_Ca8OtD4Mir6iRqKKylDJpoaW1_h6LlQNrtWbCcdiDPpJTI8PgjUxrnYvy5YvT-V5WnUxwuWYlKiJVLViecstWuKwDdwlL8oMC73NzAJDX67_WvAgl8qG5OnfeJAu4rkJWe4XovoyxCl7h5_D6bwlVhdvIC2K7VwGSnCbO3pULNiEECtJiBOQYHbvsenbPFpltqAaMCHSl8EA0t623oTl2PvPg5P16mpubNNwyoOgJXYUVlok_1kwp9ZeAO8h9d8NJpdUbHP2jPhak_3xIJIXEyyLlMtWZL-5k4-nw3vvW-9XapC2M/vGJacjG8b_S6LSL-KKmS8D_1oiFibhDR/7" target="_blank"&gt;利益率削减的&lt;/a&gt;机会很小，尽管关税的通货膨胀冲动使决策者&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/YhybhoXs1LbWN_yO-jiSSsn_JMopBlv0VaSTg0Ovu984DV88qFv3VYdWwAp8ZSSj6R-9jyb4jxdkzveHioX-Nkep_XX3aymMnodRIDHMPr0wwWaSjX9ljSdMmpFMWR6zi3pssiWdQLt7JDDYwaL7x6Edyr7jhuXzxCAINXVFywaaxMV1TrQ9iQ0XfJh0i3Nypo2Q7xLNcCMFsUbMnXe9L7oT1yiLtassX_nhfAM6v_vynwtTr5Mmm1K2g-hQyUVa9SdKTRosJGzSqoZ9zqD2BHUk7A1u9H3YYKEbmx0NynNp7pqFnXPmi1D834Gq6H09-ufc51GfSdK3IlLx61-gHqx9Vv2R6ZWlXprzIka17ibyppQVm_Eozhj_73w/DkBFpzSx2mhTfXtwTNkWoDRuo7vorZCQ/7" target="_blank"&gt;处于艰难的位置&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; RSM US LLP的首席经济学家约瑟夫·布鲁苏埃拉斯（Joseph Brusuelas）警告说，这一举动提高了经济&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/lmI3er_wr17h1ZgjuHxjiQvufddjPUPlcp55xkS2pZHJj3UfjUuZ9bo-8iUWXxCgkj47QT7VK3RbuRR4mwqVMbKRYk5jptohKZQp7U-tS4uOSXQKrRONKrYe1hQYPFAkEcGG0IlOOH8QO99zEjlkdoRoBnUGMYqYo_67zMjdugCOGxvkYV-rqc85nlHt9gy7cm-uu4pvpbhHejepFY3kzHJWcPLG7-xDe_Dj_-IvPPc_nHGK3XsPNJgNZKcOC7ZfFh4nKbtBnjzMQpOnXzyNvA0mjymbEx4wbWUX8mi99cV8ksfo7RrkvVtuRXfrKoCzild3mkVCNLSVhXIRhS4wr82IsPkSJ6pdISIjWft1GrvGHw6K5NI2IFyxoBA/PPNAjUXQevcN-aqDykvH04ZJBzFGw8g4/7" target="_blank"&gt;衰退&lt;/a&gt;的可能性，这一观点可能在未来几天被许多人分享。对于其他国家来说，特朗普的举动禁止出口重大命中，以及对政府在自己的国家增强国内需求的升级压力。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;在美国，也将需要刺激，财政部长斯科特·贝森特（Scott Bessent）在彭博电视台（Bloomberg TV）上表示，他的主要重点将与国会合作扩大和扩大2017年特朗普的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/raWgsMdpogvn9tbqz6dqulluKBEOtS4AS7bFr7_eDjQQpWgwypMDIfeKHuDuOKJmB2in8zMEMtUWCG6HK7XFT1O_djlTzJ8S89dSty8KIueV_s8EtyEqEHnUah2vVFTNKnUpULGAMJeBt5RP-JDEPykCQCrpp_Roy_FtjsGFiYckVU0YZ9eT5ANhfNMrWMlc7VoVmsR0bs1KxdS9qc_b-PDR_nHTr4FXbdvEIc7oiDiSNDVu-2vu2nKQ5j-AYJC2WzY8WqpgF5rN_zvJzOf24JuAGA2euwAW4r9LDcEXhOCqk2OsWedxh_XJN90wDB976_OslnKWkWY_ApxY4LWMjnLjjOSkQEShR8ctTd-Wzoz4OOCvdFC6znDEvac/OEzBgVWfFHJ6EcWEvM9n228LfseKWxHR/7" target="_blank"&gt;减税税&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;至于贸易协议以降低新的关税利率？他指出，政府“让事情安定一段时间”。同时，他警告说：“我不会试图报复”，并暗示特朗普可能会采取进一步的行动。他谈到新的关税率时说：“这是禁止报复的数字的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/ek_kBIieQRnPW4DniR5H7N8Ukc8ixAIiSyUHPh_kQwLsW20AhiB5DHrbRkR7p66D2MnFv1X5fQKcxWlFPG2_YION3DolGa2UV4cmymdIAZIyWqLVWkUGBQ7moDymow5nzZ7_21mM1EDx_M1aUD6peUsJzz8p9QqRRYdsNGMdyydcr0vB6kbC6eb3bZOYH3j6_f526iv_M-XhMYQ_m4avw3Nbq2k0IOv4l-oazGvSNpNwVSdBFlpBjZOZyhj5SG6CFjK9FT-ug87IlOwzl8yBnCDfC4hvefnAVKCR4Y5wvwYvgXNT8QU5EU0F4R2HKHOHqHeLbanN49E6vLbkj7VmdiODNwecuLQWW5H71_hyOHxIiyp_6WbkuEoO6G4/wA1pR9QrXXypZaZhX-44xvY4hH6xXSFv/7" target="_blank"&gt;高端&lt;/a&gt;。”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;有关更多信息，&lt;/em&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/2_P7snIBm_pqQQ9IFFCLiPh6oA0KVLnGLtYljX3b2ewfKETG36oN76mBptyiauuIp5AR21XAtrSK-yKixpUuW-jLuJeDxeC4dQQo-f_pmzM_qeBCCNaM8mg0Ay2NnWGsx1k-7nXiutzltKbkGdYnfu9gQQTy3jpUnne3a5LyXSiRzRO56NEVnJpRKMG_rn9BuAw5jd9gKlQvEh11sMj9OMDg-Hr3j6hsDXqq3vobifVwm8AmwLSO8C9C-570393tjB9vgiwr2XtiR_672eNpccp1gRAeJdhuM9JvlPtOEa1bfzYwDXFES6U5iRc6TdrLCVXMBx_1on6Qi0glBeR3UGGosrgkP_6KMvvlVwezRzxY-UUvkNdMUiIB4HU/804LwjIX8CY3Ikx80MCitMHASypsPuJE/7" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;em&gt;请订阅供应线&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt;，这是我们跟踪全球贸易的每日新闻通讯。&lt;/em&gt; &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="auto"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td align="center" colspan="2" style="padding: 0