I3qSqloNrYrdeEZHBS70dLoRmB-ivl2mmpzrVn4c4TmcB4rCP0uE-EGmYcqkegAklyNd7eCoFHyQN3kbDQh0Mh5izLAwXvvS1Da10tIh38E9MGfS45He2e7nEGUGxJsbKjVqZzqUDIigg57r9XQ-NYlE3pwAZqqZT1vNDzlMOLksLGNMvzYoQ/yCQCCtei9ZjfvKG5wVo6_V6xzIS9LQTC/7" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;一个五个月的低点&lt;/a&gt;，投资者将财政债券作为天堂扣除，日元加强了。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;大众计划向运送到美国的车辆的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/S0VR4Pu5elTaEZ8L9jMb8UUXClLdeeF6hpAtftOGcaNxe5FOdueE7OCgylcdqNVDL_cXAniYc3KaEtwTNX39LK_OD2D7jFp61DwyvnTMkFikFBNraaNUc5vCtM9f-TpEt2SOdcgtl_MY-K0Vdr7PMvPMZkBqiHCJkkxWou0dpOVbYxhN5liGZgh07jHlj1fNH_CFjJ2xkpo2ebyvmtmKv7KPOeXzbz7XoqNpYXrDty2C5tx81jm9VE3hKXQbMlOQyoEr5LLnqUnGwgF_n53jtvzhsglHSW4dRmgBMoCNDMISGkBIyRNpIjCtWkq_u31R55q6VTuM7tPdcAbmug_sPaILRadCDTSFa5sRZf2Zo1rTrsSFRbWQt0UtV20/n4jZONxiOeMYBRZ678lBKl9t3jC2tk3-/7" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;标价增加进口费&lt;/a&gt;，这表明特朗普的25％自动关税将立即对欧洲最大的汽车制造商产生影响。同时，法国希望欧盟通过&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/ARN2a0IlZ9kURO5ihX_7Zs4yOrqPL5CcN-OU0Hx44QiV3Ep-W2I6NB7Jp3LERSwF6VgwW3RA3iokv8JiYBg0g5v6sZeSw9UlJ2xUDkDHUB9ay2HK4YkEAxMgSC5UaKv-S0gMznghl3bWL7nN19b97IzBcTyqEqN6CbmD_GQGRUWCSaRSVQGjRrsoBQMqbZxrokWNp7RiucRCEdNurlEkwc4sONuyu1igBz5-B_3fl9RoCq8V0DoO9Bv1czVBWzhbe0ca3x4S_5Rc6BmWeJWdIQDm3aTdxUKc1EXskpoDEfrcC2hftA39snC9z157SWrt6sIoYAtZvt-JBXKLQ-CefeAiAXcvIGdYMk07KoKDxY_iPzxFHoipDXm44DI/wVWBiiSxS1qLmI4s38r8apeMWGTWx8zy/7" target="_blank"&gt;击中美国科技公司&lt;/a&gt;来进行报复。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;参议院共和党人推出了预算蓝图&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/OziUlTL2ETzSSY2fOTfZ0ueNj1onklidvPfExOeU8n68Ng5CgvqZQ3KY34e4SGo19hhwCvmd-g_REg4QoRvs6V6lKYUG0jfKoSsSawmaPbIpxuuJAqowJ30j19YVSdAXG7SwFQ312GuHV33KgCw_qxCaL9dn9PcChpaLSkLIhquYB8SCVCxKbPWrnljgYEdWhadt_hgPseleyqsuTJ91zFWfU9sN-ZAhH-2FFnbESc04H2YYMIHjIpiseYY-m9nlGQWwPWq6yL-4x7lNFvkYz60SxGHg_0kSkoiAyoeYhT9CREHmezhXmxummyzn08-TcXWMsMtM70q-gWi9dgJZbO8OxPYb8jkwiwAXCf-buenNdU8gshFzEB9IMCU/AAdhz-E-1SDDIDY87weeHH0OfFxbQrYo/7" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;，以快速续签&lt;/a&gt;唐纳德·特朗普的减税措施，并增加了国家借贷限额。参议院多数党领袖约翰·图恩（John Thune）说，他不确定自己是否有选票可以通过这项措施。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/tCmsgpIIDwrU_TduKmnxl7hIz0hDPe7gTclyZDDrBbNd4IgX_2qZvZfcaVX4Q2p3os1VslXMEVn9hAcWsd9JqpY21j3J80ipc-eivaiZLX2LATeYAI3dxlMIWLmRCa5iua_mqD8I7jj9ouJC7sjUVGCaUdCtDiDg5CgWWYnTuYqQT141W8_tFzCChaIy4Qh1QvzXIlpTAKdLmvacYugIgxKs2Xh5qNSj5ugwVOdFlq4wAgjAOp7PXwP4wh2e6SAnSSXYxF5kmfKB6Sb_GofqS-QLdpbvOzJGs81PW5tX8USuLjo8QYfexAMlBl29F8MuyIKzReRibfLSbdyZ3FqP-USYIb7vsREG0VWXQiqkoqW3dg_Shh2-cONOuVQ/TiU0OoZ98VZZigJXMwqT5j_qPKOPB0XN/7" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;Tiktok周六截止日期的几天前，找到买家&lt;/a&gt;或被关闭其最大市场，视频应用程序的潜在结果列表的列表更长了。 Amazon.com成为最新的大牌，涉足竞争，向白宫提交了一旦价值600亿美元的企业购买。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/1pR0uDek2RUqbA7Vy994AEf9RyCDs7rVROHOJagDPfRfSW_3YS_HvcgnvhWylBe6rVYFahB78I_Lccmr4q-hOUR4CuYFSiNS2Vl3zppi8Knh9drIjOf8DwYv4VgtlLeS4BWFo-7X2JH3E8CyRv8ixR5XLnqGd1K9KNfe_-fssMUvkTs-q11hmbBGhG-R-QshoFX7tmUKJQ_epLI69xAxbyyhf2yyyULLtgt2ITfhy_0UW4AdiHjQXYZ4M9mXreWfs6QL5YTT3leLyqTqaEkHBwJE1lao6YCSNpIqFMMb1dJUg8F0gOmtOhEwjaJ_X-RQxMjs_VV6I6jfbrLMGDBe9tumIUsKTJRquBpDS1PQ8WNLFq_ZHeBElvBvoaQ/tWglD0HDBzeGBPvMdc5TyLiLoWsT4mhf/7" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;《特朗普&lt;/a&gt;：特朗普：主持人斯蒂芬妮·佛兰德斯》的最新一集中，《金融时报》首席经济学评论员马丁·沃尔夫（Martin Wolf）也加入了。美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）认为，当前的全球贸易体系对美国不公平，关税是平衡规模的工具。但是世界如何到达这一点？在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/EiVJNXk71XQMGipoZSb5lX1RhAO6CqncjeT345pn-aqPqBunnOZrkUX96oETjJgnlhurJhmGGCMSl14f_CnKpw4NyLnhjq-dsUv56qaQ0uw5dOVA29VPejYbIkGmeFnusGzujpozvJofc8P2V6LoTTlU8Yo27WDzoezjqqMa5raiB__hwk4p-oqwYyZfHSM--HFwENXf4Q0zO9zSHgPIySIYvn_7UEV5AsXeAj0SlpO45Ue2k4OQpLG1Oq9lmlVkDUOs4m5qxvmmeviaCdz27faT7SUZliaHfFtgFNT0IN6egKC-bgNvihM2BBrwV_A2DW5B0ep-Jlqz243OpR9eiKvDNSUTNklSHeDn7R_h8q3FuWjNtAmTXTLP7tykoIJd-5c_wsUwty_wjs2ehMG2u2T52Wz0qZS89ZGW971Di4Iy0Sk6MZgwBEhpugnjNZxVxdfj2RI0Ay