ng style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;Wayfair&lt;/strong&gt;的股票下跌14％。 - &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/uAL2vIXxVtIeW7j9A1wbUqNWT6kMQ0WrUA81bmBtC_uLwlGeW02eKo7QHylY9g82br67EAomfh9z5dQ75RbqLTFRcp7qobwFNOwcoPzqvwCPLzCkkuawfFCpNETi9Fun6XEvPPEFwzhAhuUl5CBJ0mSf48O0oObTOtfd1kFf30WU6fcFJ4HvuEV8ETpeVn59hfxigbirJlN2-t9ud9ZT1SlvQMlmfsVcwZj0iEMT63Phdn63oBWZ2QGbE282yIj6wFI4rsTA1-PBVElEIdJW-g9NgaQ_k5_xNObzfpveBdzt_dqXriKbFrLQQiTIL3X39k1x3X8EvcCw6o-Z0oaU3EYHKYBeNj8hvHPRkaXeV-Tg9R6mUABP1L-So5Q/yaBNEVKTewYZeDeTSTS9v8zznv48Gdq8/7" target="_blank" title="万维网"&gt;&lt;em&gt;subrat patnaik&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 20px 10px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;center&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/m-jFiUVSboWSwCOFKuRbigXxho0xn4oWHlvxtBc7CB4nZIsxqiXdQOvVZI3iShsFCCDt10r5yviISj2FTscYw12fULywpkbSsTZpz1coGUhUmF2U_2RAZ4uoHIWJVJY7Qj0pRv9fAC2pY_tflUuSmKA0BVGq1ZwOaBdpxxkeZu2FVZdOvVZB_Yt0tTGm4tdJZVheBZkaCL2eQUMdbxnEyCaotXJD3nNPPUbK35DIg1bFMA7_ijcDbFBtat7kDwONn1g_D4AWtUWMG474zqCyZLZVqXaOSYjMo9TPhVxGQpaUzJxwG7tSdIgWYvZp9fJTAQOReEaaZ1kanH9Q0g14ND_xnaP0KsoyTbSnwgjD0J6tEckAKik54LT4B5nRZyklTXTUjykGk3beCOa-nLaJyx-x/vDuNUmZOKOAnRvNfwOXg06G173lqSVvi/7" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="The Stock Movers Podcast: Five minutes on the day's stock market winners and losers. Click here to listen on apple podcasts" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3EdW0DXt4Xk/v0/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="股票播客播客：当天的股市获奖者和失败者五分钟。单击此处收听Apple播客" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3EdW0DXt4Xk/v0/-1x-1.png" 