NjEJdWYMy5QPgEZSUfmbrB/7" title="大量基于"&gt;指控基于&lt;/a&gt;其他国家与美国的贸易盈余。他再次向诸如药物，半导体，木材和铜等领域的职责发出了信号。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/gX_UNZg-SNYZs_ynySnSePdxMwDeIhC_bK33JSRzfZrC8garfYybgVO0MvIcRNXKWHGqH44ozcADeGRANoLn7psTKTJ-pvcWtbyGd02Dfir1kmE_1ZwGaNzcTo4srcfDDmpa7UUDGzV7Zyb5gFrNLWy4ZOL8XbwBEB1HIAXD8yza_-67taOBb7IELRcDn5j35RZgrE-i471-VxPhELPe6UGzMPPLaNMt562NfsIGZ3rhiTdO4ydDSrUZ5qp4GHgGr6g_0HjrQ1I0OeEzK0VuE27emVeiRPPLpZ2AurqAZGVI9nMg0lPWHvHcaTHwwjkEOBJLa4bEDBM0A4JanCT784C5tdbM4TtzGj4RRd4MAAift7Go7VZJOsYDnwI/sQGxMKLP36clOtvohLoNAlWJw980HNZ4/7" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iZS78si6xC_A/v0/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iZS78si6xC_A/v0/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;国际反应是迅速的&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;，与美国最大的贸易伙伴欧洲联盟，如果与特朗普政府进行谈判以减少征税的失败， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/oeiEbsMkD0QVWvmGJZu88N0qyUgKEwPkfH5n5RHCynJvl_IF1JSIOV56gYkJKvt_Pjo2j6UysQoQX9Gs6lSmdUmFM0DkGhoeXZw8h85Sz1OVy_Hxo2eSaUtb43lP1HVdu3qY88N9acVWiJ8NbiEUgZVms8TazsZXx_-uKRNLD5VOZcPx_K1fnmdKr9xH92reInI47osEVBsgNlFs_3n1_St2E3aXpIH1VCsUx4AkTavzLJm9_Pmo5sUnR3WOFfkSdhjtqKkYuYKode_2lAVSj9zYWENeBiHU8PxARfFhWpT_91z2QMQe0eDX7sQnbma3mSeiIBK_Y9jzfY-ipHlfaN4k9JCOadqojND7wWIcvnhBOqkS-sTzJdOUQFc/vkg2Qms5tROkFWzbxgetulOhncnInAf8/7" title="发誓要进行报复"&gt;则誓言要进行报复&lt;/a&gt;。中国敦促华盛顿&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/jyfhPax_mamb5QTKLIHJo2oPFcp